div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>ΝΕΩΝ\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>ΔΟΝΑΚΟΣ\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ΝΕΩΝ&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Σ\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>ΔΟΝΑ[.]ΟΣ\u003Cbr id=\"al5-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;((Ε))&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Κ\u003Cbr id=\"al6-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>Δ&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \u003Cbr id=\"al7-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">7\u003C/span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \u003Cem dir=\"ltr\">\u003Cspan class=\"smaller\">vacat \u003C/span>\u003C/em>\u003Cbr id=\"al8-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">8\u003C/span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \u003Cem dir=\"ltr\">\u003Cspan class=\"smaller\">vacat \u003C/span>\u003C/em>\u003Cbr id=\"al9-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">9\u003C/span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Σ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Text after Copani 2014 with slight changes based on photograph\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Neon son of Donax\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The first two lines have the clear and standard form of a simple funerary stele. The complication arises with the increasingly illegible, irregular and seemingly incoherent letters which follow from line 3, and which seem in part at least to repeat the material of lines 1-2. Copani proposes that it should perhaps be understood as some sort of 'writing exercise' by a second, less-skilled lapicide, although this seems peculiar on a funerary stele.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Di Stefano 2013 30 ph \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002031\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002031\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Copani 2014 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002644\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002644\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">\u003Cp>The first two lines show neat broad regular letters of late classical/early hellenistic date: N with raised right hasta; E with shorter middle bar; omega large and open with short horizontal tails; sigma with open top and bottom strokes, alpha broad with straight bar. After line 2 the letters become more irregular\u003C/p> Line 1-2  25-30  Interlineation line 1 to 2    \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence.  \u003C/div>",[192,195,198,201,204,207,210,213],{"id":193,"html":194},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa; edition source: \u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/WE5GH2TN\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/WE5GH2TN\u003C/a>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"la\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>Νέων \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>Δόνακος \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>Νέων \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\">(vac.2)\u003C/span> Σ \u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>Δόνα[κ]ος \u003Cbr id=\"al5-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\">(vac.2)\u003C/span>((Ε))\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\">(vac.3)\u003C/span>Κ \u003Cbr id=\"al6-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>Δ\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\">(vac.6)\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al7-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">7\u003C/span>\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\">(vac.)\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al8-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">8\u003C/span>\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\">(vac.)\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al9-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">9\u003C/span>\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\">(vac.5)\u003C/span>Σ \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa; edition source: \u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/WE5GH2TN\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/WE5GH2TN\u003C/a>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>ΝΕΩΝ\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>ΔΟΝΑΚΟΣ\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ΝΕΩΝ&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Σ\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>ΔΟΝΑ[.]ΟΣ\u003Cbr id=\"al5-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;((Ε))&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Κ\u003Cbr id=\"al6-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>Δ&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nb