/epig10002644\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002644\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":211,"html":212},"handnote","\u003Cp>The first two lines show neat broad regular letters of late classical/early hellenistic date: N with raised right hasta; E with shorter middle bar; omega large and open with short horizontal tails; sigma with open top and bottom strokes, alpha broad with straight bar. After line 2 the letters become more irregular\u003C/p> Line 1-2  25-30  Interlineation line 1 to 2    ",{"id":214,"html":215},"license"," Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence.  ",[217,219,223,224],{"html":218},"Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa; edition source: \u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/WE5GH2TN\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/WE5GH2TN\u003C/a>",{"id":220,"lang":221,"html":222},"edition-interpretive","la","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>Νέων \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>Δόνακος \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>Νέων \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\">(vac.2)\u003C/span> Σ \u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>Δόνα[κ]ος \u003Cbr id=\"al5-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\">(vac.2)\u003C/span>((Ε))\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\">(vac.3)\u003C/span>Κ \u003Cbr id=\"al6-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>Δ\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\">(vac.6)\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al7-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">7\u003C/span>\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\">(vac.)\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al8-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">8\u003C/span>\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\">(vac.)\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al9-interpretive