erial>\n                                    \u003CobjectType ana=\"#object.stele\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/objtyp/lod/250\">stele\u003C/objectType>\n                                    \u003Cdimensions>\u003C!--Copani-->\n                                        \u003Cheight unit=\"cm\">50\u003C/height>\n                                        \u003Cwidth unit=\"cm\">30\u003C/width>\n                                        \u003Cdepth unit=\"cm\">18\u003C/depth>\n                                    \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003C/support>\n                                \u003Ccondition ana=\"#condition.damaged\"/>\n\t\t    \u003C/supportDesc>\n                            \u003ClayoutDesc>\n                                \u003Clayout>\u003Cp>The first two lines are centred and regular, but increasingly irregular thereafter.\u003C/p>\n                                    \u003Crs ana=\"#execution.chiselled\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/writing/lod/1\">chiselled\u003C/rs>\n                                \t\u003Cdamage ana=\"#text_condition.partly_illegible\"/>\n\t\t\t\u003C/layout>\n                            \u003C/layoutDesc>\n                        \u003C/objectDesc>\n                        \u003ChandDesc>\n                            \u003ChandNote>\u003Cp>The first two lines show neat broad regular letters of late classical/early hellenistic date: N with raised right hasta; E with shorter middle bar; omega large and open with short horizontal tails; sigma with open top and bottom strokes, alpha broad with straight bar. After line 2 the letters become more irregular\u003C/p>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line1\" to=\"line2\">Line 1-2\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"letterHeight\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\" atLeast=\"25\" atMost=\"30\">25-30\u003C/height>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line1\" to=\"line2\">Interlineation line 1 to 2\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"interlinear\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\"/>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                            \u003C/handNote>\n                        \u003C/handDesc>\n                    \u003C/physDesc>\n                    \u003Chistory>\n                        \u003Corigin>\n                            \u003CorigPlace>\n                                \u003CplaceName type=\"ancient\" ref=\"http://pleiades.stoa.org/places/462126\">Kamarina\u003C/placeName>\t\t\n                                \u003CplaceName type=\"modern\" ref=\"http://sws.geonames.org/6540853\">Santa Croce Camerina\u003C/placeName>\n                            \t\u003Cgeo>36.8736, 14.4507\u003C/geo>\n\t\t\u003C/origPlace>\n                            \u003CorigDate datingMethod=\"#julian\" notBefore-custom=\"-0400\" notAfter-custom=\"-0301\" evidence=\"lettering\">4th century BCE\u003C/origDate>\n                        \u003C/origin>\n                        \u003Cprovenance type=\"found\" subtype=\"discovered\">Contrada Piombo, localita Bellaccio, rescue excavation by G. Di Stefano (undated), area of a small necropolis\u003Cgeo>36.8620693,14.4817811\u003C/geo>\u003C/provenance>\u003C!-- approx location of loc. Bellaccio -->\n                        \u003Cprovenance type=\"observed\">in stores\u003C/provenance>\n                        \u003Cprovenance type=\"observed\" subtype=\"autopsied\">None\u003C/provenance>\n                        \u003Cacquisition/>\n                    \u003C/history>\n                \u003C/msDesc>\n            \u003C/sourceDesc>\n        \u003C/fileDesc>\n        \u003CencodingDesc>\n             \u003Cp>Encoded following the latest EpiDoc guidelines\u003C/p>\n             \u003Cxi:include href=\"../alists/ISicily-taxonomies.xml\">\n                 \u003Cxi:fallback>\n                     \u003Cp>Taxonomies for ISicily controlled values\u003C/p>\n                 \u003C/xi:fallback>\n             \u003C/xi:include>\n\t  \u003Cxi:include href=\"../alists/charDecl.xml\">\n\t     \u003Cxi:fallback>\n\t       \u003Cp>ISicily glyphs authority list\u003C/p>\n\t     \u003C/xi:fallback>\n\t   \u003C/xi:include>\n         \u003C/encodingDesc>\n        \u003CprofileDesc>\n            \u003CcalendarDesc>\n                \u003Ccalendar xml:id=\"julian\">\n                    \u003Cp>Julian Calendar\u003C/p>\n                \u003C/calendar>\n            \u003C/calendarDesc>\n            \u003ClangUsage>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"en\">English\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"it\">Italian\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"grc\">Ancient Greek\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"la\">Latin\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"he\">Hebrew\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"phn\">Phoenician\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"xpu\">Punic\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"osc\">Oscan\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"xly\">Elymian\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"scx\">Sikel\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"sxc\">Sikan\u003C/language>\n            \u003C/langUsage>\n            \u003CtextClass>\n                \u003Ckeywords scheme=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins.html\">\n                    \u003Cterm ana=\"#function.funerary\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins/lod/92.html\">funerary\u003C/term>\n                \u003C/keywords>\n            \u003C/textClass>\n        \u003C/profileDesc>\n        \u003CrevisionDesc status=\"draft\">\n            \u003ClistChange>\n                            \u003Cchange when=\"2016-12-03\" who=\"#JCu\">James Cummings autogenerated EpiDoc output from database\u003C/change>\n            \t   \u003Cchange when=\"2020-10-05\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova normalised Unicode\u003C/change>\n            \t   \u003Cchange when=\"2020-10-08\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova updated list of languages\u003C/change>\n            \t   \u003Cchange when=\"2020-11-26\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova restructured bibliography\u003C/change>\n\t               \u003Cchange when=\"2020-12-23\" who=\"#JP\">Updated Zenodo DOI\u003C/change>\n            \t   \u003Cchange when=\"2021-01-19\" who=\"#SS\">renumbered files, uris and references\u003C/change>\n                            \u003Cchange when=\"2021-02-23\" who=\"#VM\">Valentina Mignosa encoded text division, cleaned up the autogenerated text and checked the edition\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2025-12-18\" who=\"#JP\">Jonathan Prag revised metadata\u003C/change>\n\t\u003C/listChange>\n        \u003C/revisionDesc>\n    \u003C/teiHeader>\n    \u003Cfacsimile>\u003Csurface/>\u003C!-- \n        \u003Csurface type=\"front\">\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic003710_tiled.tif\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic003710.jpg\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n         \u003C/surface> -->\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" subtype=\"primary\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"la\" resp=\"#VM\" source=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/WE5GH2TN\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"1\"/>Νέων\n                    \u003Clb n=\"2\"/>Δόνακος\n                    \u003Clb n=\"3\"/>Νέων \u003Cspace quantity=\"2\" unit=\"character\"/> \u003Corig>Σ\u003C/orig>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"4\"/>Δόνα\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">κ\u003C/supplied>ος\n                    \u003Clb n=\"5\"/>\u003Cspace quantity=\"2\" unit=\"character\"/>\u003Corig>\u003Chi rend=\"reversed\">Ε\u003C/hi>\u003C/orig>\u003Cspace quantity=\"3\" unit=\"character\"/>\u003Corig>Κ\u003C/orig>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"6\"/>\u003Corig>Δ\u003C/orig>\u003Cspace quantity=\"6\" unit=\"character\"/>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"7\"/>\u003Cspace quantity=\"1\" unit=\"line\"/>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"8\"/>\u003Cspace quantity=\"1\" unit=\"line\"/>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"9\"/>\u003Cspace quantity=\"5\" unit=\"character\"/>\u003Corig>Σ\u003C/orig>\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\n                    \u003Capp>\n                        \u003Cnote>Text after Copani 2014 with slight changes based on photograph\u003C/note>\n                    \u003C/app>\n                \u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" resp=\"#JP\" xml:lang=\"en\">\n                \u003Cp>Neon son of Donax\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                \u003Cp>The first two lines have the clear and standard form of a simple funerary stele. The complication arises with the increasingly illegible, irregular and seemingly incoherent letters which follow from line 3, and which seem in part at least to repeat the material of lines 1-2. Copani proposes that it should perhaps be understood as some sort of 'writing exercise' by a second, less-skilled lapicide, although this seems peculiar on a funerary stele.\u003C/p>            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Di Stefano\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>2013\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>30 ph\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/E6U93JGZ\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002031\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002031\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Copani\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>2014\u003C/date>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/WE5GH2TN\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002644\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002644\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n\t   \u003ClistBibl type=\"discussion\">\u003Cbibl/>\u003C/listBibl>\n            \u003C/div>\n        \u003C/body>\n    \u003C/text>\n\u003C/TEI>\n"],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
